    bibo:startPage "333" ;
    bibo:volume "12" ;
    dc:creator "Zanata, Angela M.; Camelier, Priscila" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Characidium (Characiformes: Crenuchidae) from small coastal drainages in northeastern Brazil, with remarks on the pseudotympanum of some species of the genus" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551215>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551217>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551219> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551215>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Characidium samurai, holotype, MZUSP 108188, 46.6 mm SL, rio do Peixe, rio das Almas basin: (a) preserved specimen and (b) photographed live." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4551215/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551217>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Distribution and streams inhabited by Characidium samurai: (a) map of distribution of the new species (white dot represents the type locality), (b) type locality, Piraí do Norte, rio do Peixe, tributary of rio das Almas, (c) Nilo Peçanha, rio das Almas, and (d) Taperoá, rio Sarapuí, tributary of rio Vermelho." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4551217/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551219>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Pseudotympanum of: (a) Characidium bahiense UFBA 3470, 23.2 mm SL, (b) C. bahiense UFBA 7167, 25.4 mm SL, (c) C. samurai, paratype, UFBA 7259, 41.2 mm SL, (d) C. bimaculatum UFBA 3829, 29.5 mm SL, and (e) Characidium timbuiense UFBA 6506, 32.8 mm SL. Numbers correspond to vertebrae associated with pleural ribs. Left side, anterior to left. Overlying skin, adipose tissue and lateral-line nerve removed." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4551219/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

